@startuml
skinparam actor {
	FontSize 20
}

skinparam sequence {
	ParticipantFontSize 17
	ArrowFontSize 20
	titleFontsize 25
}

title "User Sign in"
actor User #green
App -> User: Presents Initial screen for sign up/sign in
User -> App: Provides user credentials such as user id and password
App --> AppServer: Sends the user credentials over the internet 
database Database
AppServer --> Database: Query for the User details and compare with the requested inforamtion
AppServer --> App: Response from the AppServer
App -> User: Logged in view if login was Succesful or Error message with description
@enduml
